column3: string
角色介绍
introduction
Katrina owns a bar in Bavaria that had become a rest house for some of the German troops. She has been helping the Allies secretly during this time.
Jacko Villink is an undercover agent for the Allies in Germany. He has been sent to uncover a special map, key to the allies plan to end the war.
Drago Vesilli is a German, army captain who frequents Katrina's bar to escape the stress of war. He senses something is off when Jacko enters the bar.
Edward is a kind, loving man raised by strict religious parents. When war breaks out, he decides he needs to protect his family and home.
Sergeant Jones is a hardened, straight-edge soldier. When he is tasked with training Edward into a useful recruit, his beliefs are challenged.
Carl is simple man sent to the beaches of France to fight the enemy. He teaches Edward the ropes when they are placed in the same unit.
Butch Dale is a Vietnam veteran with a chip on his shoulder. Down on his luck, he is ready to do whatever it takes to put his life back on track.
Willis McGreen spent time back in Vietnam. Instead of trying to adjust to civilian life, he has been fighting around the globe for years since.
Captain Morse is a career marine not afraid to say what he thinks whenever he wants to.
Mark Pruns have been surviving in South American jungles for the last 20 years. He knows how to live off the land and does what it takes to survive.
Matteo Bonanzo is a Peruvian general who has been fighting a revolution for the last 40 years. He has recently acquired a weapon of mass destruction.
Nicki's has been smuggling weapons for his entire career. He sees himself as a simple vendor and not responsible for the chaos his weapons cause.
Jenna Ether is Nick's girlfriend and doesn't know what he does for a living. As the truth starts slipping through the cracks, she questions their relationship.
Attiba is a young revolutionary focused on creating a better world for him, his family and the entire region which is on the brink of war.
Eros is the rookie CIA agent send on Nicki's' case. Little does he know that this lead will lead him to a worldwide network of corruption.
Boris has plenty of money and no problem eliminating enemy targets. He doesn't need to do the dirty work with his own hands, but prefers to.
Despite his wealth, Otto deeply cares about the suffering of others. He wants to help as many people as possible.
Louisa is a teenage Jewish worker at Otto's factory. She was orphaned when her parents were taken to a camp.
Heinrich Vimmler is an SS officer with a deep hatred of other people and cultures. He is a tiny, vindictive man with nothing to live for.
Sergeant Ranke just finished another war with his squad hoping to take a break from the killing to get back to his old life when Mrs. Lion calls him.
Private Lion is a typical middle America farm boy thrust in the middle of the war of nations. He is the last son of nine alive.
Private Josephs is the squad clown, always quick with a joke and a smoke. He's happy as long as he's with the squad.
Private Smiggs just wants to go home. He's not happy when Sergeant Ranke asks him to go a special mission. But he can't say no.
Private Tennuci is an Italian-American soldier who misses his mother's spaghetti a whole lot.
Kenneth is a British soldier who wishes he never left home. He must be ready to give it all if he wants to make it home.
William is a hunter who has decides to go with his brother to save their countrymen. He will use his rifle skills to protect stranded soldiers.
Edward is taken along with his brother to help sail their boat after William convinces him that they need to go protect their brethren.
Timothy loves animals more than anything. When he experiences war, he cannot handle the death that surrounds him. Only animals can give him hope.
The horse has seen horrors no animals should, but remains a noble and loyal beast.
Sergeant Haynes knows this war is madness but must persevere for the crown. He is threatened by Tim's compassion but learns to embrace it.
Kellyann grew up rich but enjoyed shooting guns. but now finds herself on the run from an enemy army. A chance encounter will determine her fate.
Grant Keys is a union officer with a mean streak. When he encounters a lady in distress, he is compelled to be a better person.
Vasily is a young Russian recruit sent on his first mission fighting for the Red Army. He will soon show his prowess with a rifle.
Ludmila is a fierce woman fighting for the Red Army. A great shot, she hates the Nazis with a passion.
Comrade Potemkin is in charge of the Red Army unit tasked with defending Stalingrad. He is fiercely patriotic but worried about his soldiers.
Vladimir is a simple farm boy and Vasily's best friend. He dreams of the day he will go home to his wife.
Major Koeninger is an evil Nazi and the best sniper Germany has to offer. He will soon be challenged beyond his expectations.
Brady is an Iraq war veteran who rarely talks about his feelings or memories. He will soon discover that pushing it down is not a good solution.
Katie is Brady's wife. She grew up troubled but found someone who accepted her when she met Brady. But she soon finds out that the war changed him.
Jonas Hurite is a young man that went to war with Brady. However, since coming home from the war, they both have had a hard time adjusting.
Cade is Brady's friend from before the war. He is put in an awkward situation when he's invited to watch football with family tensions running high.
Jenny is Jonas' cheerleader girlfriend. She doesn't know what drama will ensue when she goes to her boyfriend's friend's house for an evening.
Benny is a pilot and eager to fight. When the war ends on his doorstep, he decides he has to go into the fight.
Jake and Benny enlist together but when Benny is shot down, Jake has to deal with the guilt of surviving and helping his friends family.
Liv is distraught when Benny is shot down. She blames Jake for the whole ordeal thinking he was the one who convinced him to go to war.
Kieran is a navy cook longing for a good fight. When the Japanese attack, he leads his junior officers into the fray.
Scott is just a tourist checking out the dino safari when a giant predator breaks through a fence and destroys his day.
Liz Roy is a paleontologist specializing in carnivorous beasts. She never thought she would come face to face with the animals she studied.
Mura Soul is a doctor and a dinosaur nut. He becomes a man of action when the dinosaurs break loose despite his initial demeanor.
One of the dinosaurs that has learned to trust a few humans. He decides to defend the humans instead of his own kind.
Kim is a devoted father who tries to save his daughter from the zombie apocalypse by boarding a train to a secret military base.
Hyu is Kim's daughter. Naïve and innocent, she struggles to cope with what is happening around her.
Mikey just lost his family to the dead. After seeing a father and daughter struggle to survive in the outbreak - he decides he must protect them.
Scared to lose his life, Carl is willing to do whatever it takes to survive. Even if it means sacrificing children to the zombies.
Jake is a rich boy reluctantly on a trip to America with his parents to start a new business. He perks up when he sees a pretty girl in the crowd.
Kathy is a poor girl from England who wins his ticket on the ship of dreams through a poker game. Little does she know how much her life will change.
Gary was just buying groceries for himself and his wife when the fog hit. He lived a hard life and just wants to live with his high school sweetheart.
Hannah is a single mom whose main worry in life is her daughter. She would do anything to make sure she is safe including put others at risk.
Brody is an ex-soldier who is back in his hometown trying to live a quiet life when something supernatural seems to be killing all its residents.
John is a brilliant pilot with a huge weakness. He has depression and sometimes get angry when his past is brought up.
Doris is John's wife and wants the best for him. If only he would listen.
Phil Spencer is a copilot and notices something is wrong with John during the flight. Is he brave enough to step in?
Trevor is a normal beat cop that is faced with a major disaster that lands right in the river outside his home.
Gerard has lived with his mom his entire life. When she passes away, he does not know how to cope with the loneliness.
Sophie is Gerard's first victim. He picks her because she remind him of his mother. But can he go through with it?
Detective Slurp is one of the toughest cops in town and he means business. He will stop at nothing to catch the killer.
Billy is Gerard's son who tries to ignore the deranged tendencies of his father but as a pre-teen he can't help but start forming his own opinions.
Dick is the fiercest warrior on the 7th sector. When the invasion begins, he is the only hope for people to survive.
Adrathi is an expert mechanic with incredible intelligence. She can make a device in less than 10 minutes.
Gumbo is the best pilot the sector has ever seen. If a ship needs flying, he's the guy to do it.
Dillon is a doctor who was part of the team tasked with curing cancer. When his creation mutates into a virus, he feels responsible for fixing it.
Dillon's only companion for many years - man's best friend. Roofus in an expert at taking down zombies and surviving.
Another one of the few survivors near Dillon's city. Although attractive, Jenna's only interaction with him is to trade.
Gunther is a zombified human ravaged by the virus. He loves eating flesh and hates sunlight.
Drew is an expert fisherman who has sailed the seas his whole life. He has a deep hatred for sharks and has been fighting them his whole life.
Carl is an experienced sea captain with a beautiful boat. He loves sailing rough seas especially.
Gordon is a police officer distraught by the shark attacks that have been ravaging the town lately.
Siggy Waves is a space trucker with a confident outlook. She does what it takes to get the job done and is used to traveling through space.
The spreature is an alien life form never before seen by likes of the human crew. Is it friend or foe?
Sidney is a ship pilot who was kicked out of the armed fleet for being reckless. Space trucking suits him perfectly.
Fredric is a kind-hearted man who longs for nothing more than to return to his home planet and to see his wife.
Brad is a reporter who travels the world looking for answers to what started the zombie apocalypse.
Snippy is a government official tasked with rebuilding society following the zombie infection.
Tyra is a construction worker turned army grunt. When the zombie apocalypse hit, she made her way home to find her town destroyed.
A middle classes, all he wants to do is bridge the gaps between the classes. Little does he know its been manufactured to be that way.
Justin Take is a poor 3rd class passenger who just wants to live a good life. The rich passengers are preventing him to do that.
Lister is a 3rd class man who desperately wants to get back at the passengers in the upper classes.
Cray is the train's despot, dictator and ruler - although he does it from the shadows. Only when Wilford starts making waves does he show his face.
Michael is the jock of the group. A talented football player, he is muscular, sexy and cute.
Bobby has a crush on Domi. He is an intelligent man with a lot going for him. Does he have what it takes to seduce Domi?
Domi is the full package. She is smart, beautiful and fun to be around. She is easy to flirt with but hard to be in a relationship with.
Daniela is Domi's best friend. She is the hot girl and loves teasing the boys. She enjoys attention more than anything.
Charles has just moved to the big city from his small hometown. He desperately needs a job but can't seem to fit in.
Josephine is the local girl who works at the market. She always has a kind smile ready for someone in need of comfort.
Nick is Charlie's best friend. A busy office manager, he feels the stress of modern life crushing him but doesn't know how to escape this trap.
Lana is a top model but all she wants to find a rich man to marry but has always been a hopeless romantic at heart.
James is a brilliant artist who never really knew how to make money. He has found a rich woman to live off of, but he is missing something in life.
Rachel lives upstairs to Lana, her constant swing dancing keeps Lana up at night and have a tense and heated relationship.
Charlie is a doctor that lives in the building that wants nothing to do with the drama happening above him in the apartment building.
Jimmy is a lawyer who works from home. He is a serious man but a bit bored with his life. Could a young lovely woman change that?
Mary is a stunning blonde recently arrived in New York. She is looking to make friends and have a good time.
Oscar is a greedy love doctor who sets Jimmy up with Mary. He just wants Jimmy's marriage to end.
Ram is a professional hitman. He does not mind doing what it takes to complete a job, but he is looking for a way out.
Harry is another ruthless hitman. He dreams of packing his bags and going off to Amsterdam.
Rufus is the baddest criminal in town. The one thing he cares about more than his wife is his money.
A college student who has made a few foolish choices having landing her right in the middle of a gang, hitmen and a robbery.
A career bank robber, when his heist is stolen from him, he goes on a warpath to get his revenge and his money back.
Hugh is a young, hopeless club owner who believes and problem can be solved by the power of true love.
Nicolette is a seductive cabaret dancer at a famous Paris nightclub. She is cynical and does not believe in true love, only cold, hard cash.
Vincent is a teenager smitten with Nicolette and helps her get things done around the city that she's not supposed to do.
Ricardo is a rival club owner who has a healthy competitive relationship with Hugh.
Jerome is a slimy businessman who loves to take advantage of his partners. He develops feelings for Nicolette and will stop at nothing to get her.
Cade is a rock pianist with incredible skills. He is quite frustrated since most gigs he finds are mainly playing pop songs instead of true rock.
Kylie is an aspiring actress who makes ends meet by working as a barista. She keeps going to auditions but is tired of being rejected.
Jennifer is a highly successful lady from London. She needs to stay in the country and will do whatever it takes to not be deported.
Gary is an ambitious man who decided to start working as an assistant to advance his career. He agrees to marry Jennifer to advance himself.
Dwayne is Jennifer's best friend and the one to suggest she marry an American. He'd do it himself but he's already shacked up.
Charna is jealous of Jen's success and tries to get her caught by the authorities. Will she succeed?
Christopher is the FBI officer attached to Jennifer and Gary's marriage case. Will he uncover their plot?
Jemma is a very famous Hollywood star who longs for a time where she won't be recognized constantly on the street.
Hugo is a humble entrepreneur who is trying to get his bookstore going. He just wants to be like everybody else.
Timmy is Hugh's awkward, journalist roommate. He is funny and lovable, but definitely not the cleanest guy around.
Bert is a cab driver who is growing more and more frustrated with his job. He feels he has been wronged by society and deserves more.
Caleb Drake is a famous politician running for office as New York's governor. He is running on a platform to help those in need.
Judy is a young girl who ran away from home and has nowhere else to turn. In order to survive, she turns to criminal activities on the street.
Neal is a physicist obsessed with quantum mechanics. Despite having figured out most of the universe's secrets, he still doesn't understand love.
Dr. Konrad is quite famous in his field. He loves giving long lecture about the importance of bacteria. He wishes he was a bit cooler though.
A high IQ and a ladies man. He often puts off work to go on dates when he actually should be finishing his rocket science research.
Rupert is in astronaut training not only because of his intellect but also to attract women. If only he could hold a conversation with one.
Selena is a beautiful singer/songwriter. She has just moved to the city to make a name for herself.
Gordon is a sheriff who really enjoys the outdoors. Nothing makes him happier than riding on horseback through the plains.
Jude is a farmer used to working hard on the fields each and every day. Despite all the work, he feels unhappy in life.
Farah is Gordon's wife. She is unhappy in her marriage but doesn't want to be shunned by her friends. She notices something is wrong.
Ada is Jude's wife. She knows he is hiding a secret but not sure exactly what it is.
Victor is a tourist who is looking for some excitement in his life. He has recently broken up with his girlfriend and feels vulnerable.
Jenna is a young woman who now works as a bird watcher. She had an accident a few years ago and cannot remember anything.
Garret is Jenna's best friend and extremely protective of her. He hopes she will find her way despite her terrible condition.
Harry is Jenna's father and very protective of his daughter. He wants her to have a life but doesn't know how to give it to her.
Gene is a busy office worker who never takes a moment to think or appreciate life. He needs to be reminded of how beautiful things are.
Rover is a dog that has almost than human like qualities and in fact is probably a better companion than most human beings.
Betty is Gene's wife. She is worried about how busy her husband is but notices a noticeable improvement when he brings home a dog.
Carry is a housewife but longs for more excitement. She has always had feelings for girls but never acted them out.
Dariah is a confident woman who is comfortable in her skin. When she starts falling for Carry, she is challenged by her conservative feelings.
Duke is Carry's neighbour and knows something is going on when she notices a visitor coming in and out at weird times.
Bob is a store clerk who has been trying to court Dariah for a year. He has had some success but it seems she has lost interest.
Mikel is a Russian refugee who has become friends with Carry and is actively trying to destroy the relationship out of jealousy.
Jimmy is a successful lawyer who travels a lot for work. Lonely in his hotel room, he decides to go down to the bar where he meets Rain.
Rain is a professional comedian who specializes in comedy that challenges people's core beliefs. After bombing a show, she stops by the hotel bar.
Larry is Jimmy's friend and does not approve of his relationship with Rain. He tries to get involved by sabotaging her shows.
Ann has struggled to find a job that she really cares about but has always had a tender heart.
Shifty was paralyzed during a boating accident. He struggles with finding a reason to keep on going and just wants to watch TV all the time.
Steve is Shifty's best friend and wants him to find the positive side of life. He is the one who hires Ann and asks her to take care of him.
Bob is a stock trader who pursues his goal to get rich quick by convincing people to buy stocks that will give his personal company an advantage.
Kimmy is Leo's beautiful wife. She loves her husband's wealth but despises his personality.
Toadie is an overweight man who wants to fit in with the cool guys. He has a way with numbers and discovers Bob's plan and decides to become involved.
George is a rival company's CEO. He feels like something is not right with Bob's success but can't quite figure it out.
Mia is a ballerina dancer used to playing smaller roles. When she is cast as the lead in a huge ballet, the pressure becomes too much.
Heather is the hot new dancer of the company. She is young, talented and ambitious.
Danny is the company director and wants to put on the best show possible. He is sexual and dominating in his demeanor, but very talented.
Catherine Ends is Heather's role model and used to be a very successful dancer. She is ravaged by what age has done to her.
Wilma is Mia's sister and jealous of her success. She blames her for stealing her dreams and putting her in the shadows.
Ophelia is a strong, independent woman forced into being the forced breeder of a wealthy family. She wants to break free but feels hopeless.
Father June is the man in charge of all the handmaids. He is a strict religious man who thinks the ends justifies the means.
Zuri is another independent woman who keeps getting in trouble by fighting back. She is continually tortured but the government refuses to kill her.
A police enforcer tasked with torturing Zuri. When he is asked to do the same to Ophelia, he is faced with following his own morals or the law.
Arnie is an eccentric lad who always thought he could talk his way out of any problem. Alone on an island, he won't have anybody to talk to.
Gabriel had died but was slowly coming back to life after developing superpowers. Arnie befriends him after the shock of finding a living dead man.
Modo has always dreamed of adventure. When he is given a mysterious rose bush, he answers the call and begins his journey.
Vanhansen is an ancient wizard with deep knowledge. He knows the bush must be destroyed but cannot do it himself.
A dark elf, nimble and skilled with a crossbow. He is set on finding the assassin the killed his brother.
A human turned to the streets after getting kicked out of his kingdom. With nothing left to fight for, he decides to protect the innocent.
Boron is an evil beast bent on taking over the entire world. He needs his rose bushes to do it.
Larry is a poor child bullied by his relatives. He dreams of becoming a wizard but does not know how to go about it.
Will Quigley quickly befriends Larry at the school of magic. Together they vow to have fun at all costs.
Henrietta is super popular bus her best friends are Larry and Will. She is the smartest kid in school and well respected for it.
Boldefort is an evil dude who killed Larry's brother when he was a baby. Little does he know Larry is his kryptonite.
Tosh is a troubled man whose entire life is disrupted when he discovers his time-traveling prowess.
Linda is Tosh's best friend. She suffers greatly when Tosh tries to fix his past mistakes.
No matter what Tosh do, his life nemesis, Morris, always ends up hating him.
Jimbo is Tosh's uncle. He thought he knew his nephew but has to question everything when Tosh continues to contradict himself.
Paulina is Tosh's shrink and realizes that her patient is deeply disturbed and is trying to figure out how to stop him from hurting himself.
Zach is a family father who regrets all his decisions. He wishes he could go back in time to change his life and it magically happens.
Carlos is a an attractive, young man who befriends the younger Zach when he comes back in time. His flaws help Zach realize his own.
The chosen one who will pull the axe from a tree and liberate a country from oppressive rule.
This mage is from days old trying to figure out where she stands in current politics. Ultimately, she just wants to ensure magic continues to exist.
One of King Brutus' knights known for his honor, valor and deadly skills in battle. He will stand by Brutus side no matter what.
A rival king of a rival kingdom, he wants to put Burtus down for good and take the lands and resources for himself.
Ed is a misunderstood teenager whose passion in life who just like to chop food with his hands that have knives for fingers.
The person in the town that has given Ed any benefit of the doubt and has become his tentative friend.
Ed's father who had knives for feet. He and had a great life until his father was eaten by a shark while they were at the beach one day.
A big political figure in the town. Ed fascinates her but when she tries to court him he reacts in rage. Embarrassed she tries to sabotage his life.
Mike is Peg's ex-boyfriend from years ago. He hasn't gotten over the fact they broke up and is desperately jealous of the attention she gives Ed.
An intelligent man with a peculiar condition. Born an old man, he has spent his entire life growing younger.
A morose young lady who loves a man despite all his flaws.
A promiscuous woman who can show you the world.
An old sailor with an adventurous, degenerate spirit and a good eye for talent.
The president of the United States. A crazy man with strong fortitude.
A ruthless killer dressed in gold wielding a sharp blade. He is a vampire himself but tries to fight it.
The best friend and comedic sidekick. He has a crossbow and deep knowledge.
An evil vampire hellbent on destroying humanity and farming for its blood supply.
A lovely girl who wants to do what's best for her family. But deep down, she longs for adventure.
A high school boy who gets incredibly awkward when he gets close to girls.
Miya's younger sister and a pain in the neck.
Katsu's best friend. Someone who wants the best for her friend but keeps questioning her choices.
The office flirt and a really pretty girl.
A desperate human who has been on the run from vampires his whole life. As his kind becomes rarer, the price on his head increases.
A scientist vampire who is trying to find a solution to the problem of dwindling blood supplies.
A vampire who wants what is best for his species, but thinks there must be a more sensible solution than the eradication of humans.
An evil politician who wants every human farmed for their blood.
A young child who recently moved to a new house but doesn't like it at all. That is until she finds a secret labyrinth in her backyard.
A career military man who cannot seem to find his way home. He has been lost in this maze for years.
A giant, evil faun that loves nothing more than eating the people lost in his maze.
Bane is a knight of the aging republic looking to find peace after all the war. Instead he finds himself escorting a woman to her death.
Bane's right hand man. He does not trust the woman they escort and is convinced she has magical abilities.
Rosa has been accused for the gruesome deaths of the entire town she lived in. She is manipulative and ruthless and only cares about her own survival.
The chosen princess who needs to reclaim her kingdom. She rides on dragons and takes what she wants.
The bastard child of a northern lord, he has a claim to the throne but must follow his conscience and do what's right.
A backstabbing king killer who only cares about himself. And maybe his children.
An honorable knight and good fighter, he has a claim to the throne but hides a dark secret.
A young kid who dreams of one day slaying his own dragon. His heart is turned when he meets one in real life.
A young lady with sense of adventure and great inner strength.
A friendly dragon who loves a nice snack.
An evil dragon that loves to destroy things built by humans.
Gunny is a rancher action figure equipped with lots of guns to fend for himself in the wild. He is the leader of the toys of the bedroom.
An toy manufactured for evil. He enters the world of the living with his one and only goal - to destroy humanity.
The owner of the bedroom - he has no idea what drama goes on in there while he is away at school.
Roofus, the dog next door, has extra sensory perception and often joins the toys on their excursions. On d-day, will he help toykind or humanity?
He lives next to Fred and is stealing his toys one by one to burn them in a bonfire. Will the toys figure out the mystery before it's too late?
Nero is a single dad tuna who loses his son to a strong current. He must put his entire life on hold to go and save him.
Jasper got reckless on a hunt with his dad and taken by a current deep into the unknown sea. He must befriend some other fish to stay alive.
Doris is dolphin that Nero convinces to come along with him on the journey. It is her job to keep Nero thinking clearly about the situation.
Turtle is a human boy who has a run in with Jasper after he manages to get himself stuck in a toilet on an island.
A convertible sports car who has a dream to race in the big Maine race. He's not made for professional racing but that doesn't stop him from dreaming.
Flash's friend who encourages him to follow his dreams, even if they are a little lofty.
Another one of Flash's friends. Not the sharpest tool in the shed but he's as loyal as they come.
Priya wants to survive and is ready to sacrifice herself for honor. She soons find out that what she thought was honor was something else altogether.
A handsome man who is also thrown in the combat zone and is ready to defend those he cares about.
A young girl with an innocent air - she uses her wits to survive in the battle arena. She does not want to participate but has no choice.
The beautiful man who was left behind back in Primrose's hometown. He decides to wage his own battles back at home.
A grumpy old man who misses his deceased wife. When a greedy neighbor threatens to take away the house, he must devise a plan to fight for it.
A teenager running away from home finds himself along for an adventure when the house he's hiding lifts off the ground.
A failed pirate captain in search of glorious plunder and a nice drink. Despite being a drunk, he is the most dangerous pirate of the seven seas.
A daughter of a famed pirate, she finds herself a captive of an enemy ship. When tested, it turns out she is not such a bad fighter herself.
A young crewman with noble intentions and a beautiful souls. Despite his goodness, he wants to be a pirate.
A seasoned aristocrat who wants to put an end to outlawness and pirate raids and take the booty for himself.
A rival pirate captain who wants to use mystical powers and the occult to gain dominion of the seas and Marrow's hat.
Travis grew up in a perfect world. But when he hits 20, he starts to realize something is not quite right when he sees his dead mother walking around.
Kylie is Travis's long-time girlfriend. She feels bad for Travis but values her job more than his life.
Mitch is Travis' best friend and confidant. By contract he can't tell Travis the truth, but his conscience is screaming to do the opposite.
Eddie is Travis' fake father - their fake relationship has been falling apart since Travis became a teenager.
Mika was a subject of a viral experiment that triggers an epidemic. She must fight her way through mutants to find safety with the other survivors.
Another immune subject of the experiment that fights side by side with Mika.
A guard that worked in Mika's facility. He survived the first wave of the virus and must join forces with Mika and Dimbo if he wants to get out alive.
Part of corporate security, he tries to ensure the survival of Mika or Dimbo to ensure they can be studied to create a vaccine once back in safety.
A dark hero of the night who likes nothing more than some curse words and a good fight.
An eager girl who aims to please and help out where possible.
The best helper any hero could ask for. He doesn't ask questions and has all the super gadgets you could ever need.
A juggernaut with a license to kill. Axe can take down any enemy with ease.
The discoverer of the site while on a military mission. He is accidentally bonded to a mummy in the tomb and must find a way to break it.
An archeologist sent to investigate the site. She is the only one who has enough information to figure out the mystery of the tomb.
Lucas' commanding officer who wants to use the supernatural powers of the tomb for military purposes.
1000 years ago, Sharakia, a priest, was cursed and killed after murdering one of their own. Her tomb was never meant to be opened once sealed.
An innocent girl who lives a comfortable life but is quickly pulled out of that illusion.
A renegade revolutionary who believes the end always justify the means.
A loyal police officer who starts connecting the dots and realizes he is one of the baddies.
A dystopian dictator who wants to keep a firm grip on power. He takes every chance he gets to push the common folk deeper into poverty.
An assassin with incredible skills when it comes to sneaking, climbing, fighting and stealing.
A corporate scholar trying to unlock the truth behind a mystical organization.
An older, more experienced assassin who teaches Darkblade the ropes.
A wealthy businessman who is trying to pervert an ancient ritual to increase his own power.
Cory spends most of his time alone in his room playing his uke. His family hates that he spends so much time away from them.
Cory's dead grandfather who was killed when he was just a baby. Nobody knew who had committed the crime nor knew of any motive.
Rico's widow. She fell into a deep depression when Rico died and does the minimum to survive.
Rico's murderer who has been hiding out in the village under the guise of someone else for a decade.
A raccoon with a mission who dreams of becoming an intelligence agent. Bad guys beware.
A devious hyena who cares for nothing but making fortunes for himself who gets pulled into something bigger than he can handle.
A seal who has the key to the whole mystery - if only he could remember what it was.
An evil cow who pretends to be harmless bovine but loves scheming terrible plots. Is she the most deadly of them all?
A young man eager to learn more about becoming a man but does not know how to go about doing that.
A seductive war widow who longs for a man's touch and some excitement in her tranquil life.
An evil man who seeks to fulfill himself with enforcing his power over people. He has a tendency to go after younger women.
After losing her job, Elle is forced to take an assistant job at a fashion magazine. She wants to quit but her crazy boss will not leave her alone.
Jodie is the best of the best in fashion. Her new assistant, Elle, and her inability to understand fashion triggers a dark side in her.
Tippy is one of the junior fashion editors and puts herself on the line to help Elle deal with the hell that her boss is bringing upon her.
Tim is a hidden genius that doesn't realize his potential. One day he stumbles on a philosophical problem that he answers and all is revealed.

A devoted monk who believes his passion for christ makes any crime he commits acceptable.
A crippled scholar obsessed with unlocking an ancient secret. He does not care who dies while he tries to discover this truth.
A secret agent who seems to have forgotten who he is. He must fight his way to remember where he comes from.
A German scholar who actually is a spy, but few know of it.
A seasoned leader whose knowledge knows no bounds. He will never betray his nation.
A cruel man who wants to spread death wherever he goes, and won't allow anybody to stop him.
An innocent man who finds himself on the run from intelligence agencies. He panics but is driven enough to run his way out of this situation.
An older hacker who has now turned his skills against the government he supported for so long.
A duck hunter who finds himself a target when one of his cameras captures the brutal murder of an important man.
Zane is a world-class spy who seems to be able to do nothing wrong. But he doesn't foresee the problems of neglecting his girlfriend back home.
Elaine is a highly capable woman who is set on making Zane's life hell after almost ignoring her for the past 6 months.
Stubbs is a girl that gets stuck in tough situation abroad, Zane must get her back to safety and keep her away from her kidnappers.
William is part of an international gang of kidnappers, Stubbs' family controls a lot of money and he wants some of it.
Rick is just an ordinary flower salesman who is mistaken for a criminal lawyer. He must go on the run until he can prove his innocence.
Ramira a spy sent to take Rick down, but instead she finds out the truth and falls in love. She must help him find out the truth.
Ramira's partner who has been led astray by her to help protect Rick.
Sam was the original target of the scheme that Rick gets accidentally involved in. He hopes that Rick can also get his name cleared.
A recently separated man who is bored with his life and wants some excitement. He ran away from his problems and ended in Prague to party and relax.
An absolutely stunning lady who is involved with the mob and the police. She never wanted to be a part of it but somethings aren't a real choice.
A great cop who wants to keep the order, but things get complicated when Sarah reveals her mob ties.
The biggest criminal in town. A vile man with a penchant for brutality and accidentally thinks that Aaron is a man he is not.
A secret weapon trained in the art of war, she can kill with ease but never does so unless provoked.
A brutal fighter with extreme prowess and cruelty. She will do whatever it takes to take down the enemy.
A Croatian agent who is angry at the world and wants to watch it burn.
A spy who wants to save innocent lives. He is even willing to betray his country to help protect the innocent.
